oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Horton, Lee
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This article isby no means ascientific work,but, hopefully ,a practical discussionon themutations of thepeach face LoveBird . I do notintend to write atgreat length onthe subject ofgenetics but anunderstanding of the basic inheritanceof the different color variations of thePeach Face Love Bird is necessary. Itis through this understanding and throughproper breeding programs that we areable to produce viable strains of color.
